Nach allem, was wir gebaut haben, solltest du ungefähr diese APIs haben:

# 🔐 Accounts

```text
POST /api/accounts/register/
```

User registrieren

```json
{
  "username": "max",
  "email": "max@test.de",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "customer"
}
```

---

```text
POST /api/accounts/login/
```

JWT Token holen

```json
{
  "username": "max",
  "password": "max"
}
```

---

```text
POST /api/accounts/token/refresh/
```

Token erneuern

---

```text
GET /api/accounts/me/
```

Aktuell eingeloggten User anzeigen

---

# 👤 Customers

```text
GET    /api/customers/
POST   /api/customers/
GET    /api/customers/{id}/
PUT    /api/customers/{id}/
PATCH  /api/customers/{id}/
DELETE /api/customers/{id}/
```

---

# 🚗 Vehicles

```text
GET    /api/vehicles/
POST   /api/vehicles/
GET    /api/vehicles/{id}/
PUT    /api/vehicles/{id}/
PATCH  /api/vehicles/{id}/
DELETE /api/vehicles/{id}/
```

### Suche

```text
/api/vehicles/?brand=BWM
/api/vehicles/?model=M4
/api/vehicles/?status=available
/api/vehicles/?year=2026
/api/vehicles/?search=BWM
/api/vehicles/?search=M4
```

